Abengoa Buys 1 Million Call Options on Own Shares at 21.13 Euros

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-08-02T06:20:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-02/abengoa-buys-1-million-call-options-on-own-shares-at-21-13-euros.html
Abengoa SA (ABG)  said it bought 1 million
call options on its own shares at 21.125 euros to cover its
liabilities under a 200 million-euro ($285 million) convertible
bond which matures in July 2014, the company said in a
regulatory filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  